         <abstract id="aspace_ce0767aa2aa6faa9dfd9def3750911f8">The materials consist of photographs of Yale faculty, administrators, and presidents, as well as various campus scenes and buildings. The photographs were used as illustrations in George W. Pierson's book,<title localtype="simple" render="italic">
               <part>Yale: A Short History</part>
            </title> (1976).</abstract>
    
